  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Explore Western Canada on an incredible escorted journey from sky to sea, traveling through craggy Rocky Mountain passes, glacial valleys and breathtaking National Parks. From Calgary to Vancouver you'll follow the wild paths of fur traders, gold prospectors and cowboys as you pass through charming mountain resorts, </span><span>prairie frontier towns and sophisticated port cities. Canadian wildlife is rife in the West; search for elk, mountain goats, bears and whales.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>50</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
