</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<p><em>Please note that this tour is not exclusive to Inghams and there may be guests from other tour operators. Tours and their itineraries may be subject to change. Where this becomes necessary, and where practicable, we will take the steps as outlined in clause 5 of our <a href="https://d2ysej9jnfdoyq.cloudfront.net/media/13073810/hotelplan-booking-conditions-2019_schedule-2-info.pdf">terms and conditions</a>.</em></p>]]></description>
